headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Car Meet Membership Bonuses
content:
If you haven’t already, visit the LS Car Meet by August 18 to receive a rare LS Customs Varsity Jacket, free of charge. All LS Car Meet Members who reach — or have already reached — Reputation Level 20 by that time will get a bonus to the tune of GTA$250K.

Meanwhile, winning a race in the Street Race Series this week will earn you the Obey Tee and bragging rights. All awards will be delivered within 72 hours of completion.
